						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/china-2/" rel="tag">china</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/futures/" rel="tag">futures</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/silver/" rel="tag">Silver</a></span>					</p>
