				<div class="entry">

					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/04/11/gatas-bill-murphy-sees-non-stop-government-goldsilver-manipulation-april-10-2012/">Gata’s Bill Murphy Sees Non-Stop Government Gold/Silver Manipulation – April 10,&nbsp;2012</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">April 11, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/04/11/gatas-bill-murphy-sees-non-stop-government-goldsilver-manipulation-april-10-2012/#respond" title="Comment on Gata’s Bill Murphy Sees Non-Stop Government Gold/Silver Manipulation – April 10,&nbsp;2012">Leave a comment</a></span>
