			<div class="post-941 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-fiat-currency category-gold category-hft category-trading tag-biderman tag-charles-biderman tag-gold-2 tag-liquidity tag-manipulation tag-rigged-markets tag-silver">

				<div class="entry">

					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/04/01/charles-biderman-the-problem-with-rigged-markets/">Charles Biderman: The Problem with Rigged&nbsp;Markets</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">April 1, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/04/01/charles-biderman-the-problem-with-rigged-markets/#respond" title="Comment on Charles Biderman: The Problem with Rigged&nbsp;Markets">Leave a comment</a></span>
																				</p>
					</div>

