			<div class="post-909 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-gold category-silver tag-gold-2 tag-silver">

				<div class="entry">

					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/03/31/silver-manipulation-acknowledged-by-government-christian-garcia-goldsilver-com-slv/">Silver Manipulation Acknowledged By Government Christian Garcia GoldSilver.com&nbsp;$SLV</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">March 31, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/03/31/silver-manipulation-acknowledged-by-government-christian-garcia-goldsilver-com-slv/#respond" title="Comment on Silver Manipulation Acknowledged By Government Christian Garcia GoldSilver.com&nbsp;$SLV">Leave a comment</a></span>
