				<div class="post-meta">
					<p>
						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/gold/" rel="category tag">Gold</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/silver/" rel="category tag">Silver</a></span>
						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/gold-2/" rel="tag">GOLD</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/silver/" rel="tag">Silver</a></span>					</p>
